A Provider-Centric Perspective

Explore the journey of becoming an Akash Network cloud provider, from preparing your infrastructure to managing leases on the Supercloud platform. Follow these six stages to offer your Kubernetes clusters and join the Akash ecosystem.

Praetor App makes it simple to become an Akash Network cloud provider. Instead of utilizing the Command-line Interface, you can use a streamlined UI to become a provider.

When offering compute power to Akash’s network, you support the decentralized cloud while earning rewards. Use the Praetor Calculator to estimate potential earnings based on current rates.
